Paramedics are on the scene. Courtesy #DStv403 DURBAN - A man believed to be in his 20's was shot multiple times outside Westville Mall on Friday. The man was shot while travelling in his vehicle with a passenger, who also sustained minor injuries. READ: Task team to probe Benoni shooting The man was stabilised on the scene by paramedics and rushed to a nearby hospital for further care. Rescue Care's Gareth Jamieson says the man sustained multiple critical gunshot wounds to his entire body. Watch the video above for more on this story.